 />\n遇襲記者︰好似屍殺列車<br />\n不滿警黑合作 民政局職員疑罷工<br />\n國際將香港新疆相提並論<br />\n台灣不再信一國兩制謊言<br />\n警再開槍射頭 示威者重創<br />\n記者遭速龍舉槍棍指嚇<br />\n濃煙下槍聲四起 示威者變活靶<br />\n警不作為 黑幫肆虐元、屯、荃 變死城"},{"pid":"369ae153b1ffbb4dd0dfe1b21206593cf084a38a","tid":1356933,"uid":36833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:34:22.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3554f12ac38a19117734673fd185e160e4aeebf7","tid":1356933,"uid":257527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連還炒車， 屌"},{"pid":"0619eaadc57bab5962eff7461898a0c3a3d1115c","tid":1356933,"uid":21825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:35:22.000Z","msg":"唔好再推喇，出面已經有幾個同類post"},{"pid":"e94791cadf3ecc83086f2621b59ec5b1b6b25ff7","tid":1356933,"uid":285894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"Ann姐出嚟講嘢啦"},{"pid":"fe6bdc4299259a61c8508903783515480f3f16d1","tid":1356933,"uid":265113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T15:36:45.000Z","msg":"推"}]}